      "raw_text": "VULCAN. July 30-Reports from\nthis section of the Big Bend coun-\ntry indicate that many farmers are\nplanning to cut their wheat crops\nfor hay. as the yield Is so light\nas to be not worth threshing. Ex-\ntreme dry and hot weather Is the\ncause. In the vicinity OF Quincy\nthe cvrop will average 20 bushels\nto the acre."
